questions.question:
Rewrite this index-based loop as an idiomatic iterator chain:

```rust
let mut result = Vec::new();
for i in 0..numbers.len() {
    if numbers[i] % 2 == 0 {
        result.push(numbers[i] * 3);
    }
}
```

answer_key.full_credit:
```rust
let result: Vec<i32> = numbers.iter()
    .filter(|&&n| n % 2 == 0)
    .map(|&n| n * 3)
    .collect();
```
